<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA1">
<l>tirukkaṇṭēṉ poṉmēṉi kaṇṭēṉ ṟikaḻu</l>
<l>marukka ṉaṇiniṟamuṅ kaṇṭēṉ – cerukkiḷarum</l>
<l>poṉṉāḻi kaṇṭēṉ puricaṅkam kaikkaṇṭē</l>
<l>ṉeṉṉāḻi vaṇṇaṉpā liṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw Śrī, I saw the golden body, I saw all of</l>
<l>the adorning colour of the shining sun, I saw</l>
<l>the golden disk that emerges in battles, I saw the spiralling conch in the hand</l>
<l>– [all] on my [lord] with the colour of the ocean today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
